  "body": "<img alt=\"6a-IMG_3624.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/00bad3f5c1493d53.jpg?v=1782537815\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"6b-IMG_1962.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1997803687ad0686.jpg?v=1782537818\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6c-IMG_1966.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8bfe121a4439da72.jpg?v=1782537821\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6d-IMG_1965.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7859275fc1791dfb.jpg?v=1782537824\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6e-IMG_1971.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9e01c3db06a78e84.jpg?v=1782537826\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6f-IMG_1974.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/06014ac7cbf3cb5b.jpg?v=1782537829\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6g-IMG_1978.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/53327615529f8492.jpg?v=1782537832\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6h-IMG_1967.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/22071a1e50527483.jpg?v=1782537835\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>While in Florida, I saw my ball garland for the first time at <a href=\"http://whimsodoodle.com/\">Whim So Doodle</a>. I got excited and had to take some cheesy photos. I also had to get it so I could come home and freshen up my desk area.I gathered together a bunch of items, mostly from my <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=stitched&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fsearch%2Easpx%3FKeywords%3Damy%2Btangerine%2Bstitched%2B2014\">Stitched</a> collection. Though the set up was looking good, it was time to change it up a little bit.The felt garland is available online <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=33086&amp;m=7429&amp;afftrack=garland&amp;urllink=store%2Escrapbook%2Ecom%2Fac%2D368979%2Ehtml\">here</a> and <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=garland&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fproduct%2Easpx%3Fid%3D312644\">here</a>.</p><p>What have you created from <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=stitched&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fsearch%2Easpx%3FKeywords%3Damy%2Btangerine%2Bstitched%2B2014\">Stitched</a> other than paper projects?</p>"
